      "writtenOn": "2015-10-14T01:03:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I can\u0027t just overload getBool because a string literal \"like this one\" implicit casts to bool instead of std::string.\n\nIt is possible to call the write overload by explicitly casting to string, but that\u0027s a gotcha that\u0027ll happen sooner than later.",
